string-array.item: 3. Players level $0 and up can sign up for the Championship Cup.
4. After the Championship begins, the system will randomly assign 1-on-1 matches. Winners will go on to more rounds, until the Final 32 are determined.

5. 32 competitors will enter the Finals. Finals are divided into First and Second Divisions. Both Divisions will carry out one round of 1-on-1 battles per day, with winners proceeding to the next round. The First and Second Division winners will then face each other in the Championship Match.
6. Alliance equipment cannot be used in the Championship, but alliance technology boosts will take effect.

string-array.name: gametips
string-array.item: Click your player avatar to change your password.
Reset will clear all game information. Click your player avatar to find the reset option.
If you forgot your password, you can find the retrieve option on the opening screen.
Items bought from the shop will be equipped automatically.
To change your equipment, click on the altar (the golden statue) and select items to equip.
"To change spells, click the altar (the golden statue) and select the spells you'd like."
Complete daily task to earn valuable spar and mojo rewards!
Your hero gains honor by killing enemies. Honor points can be exchanged for other powers at the altar.
Plants will increase your population limit and occasionally drop resources by surprise.
Visit your friends to collect fallen resources.
You can earn a little surprise by visiting friends and helping them open their treasure chest.
While visiting friends, you can also help speed up their resource production.
While visiting friends, you can help them produce soldiers and resources.
You will get a free lottery spin after a set period of time.
During the protection stage, no troops will be lost in battle.
Conquest time varies depending on different geographical locations.
After a successful conquest, you can collect taxes from your little prisoner.
After a successful conquest, you will have an endearing new slave to produce resources for you.
"You can check your enemy's formation before attempting to win a castle back."
Retreating from a battle in the arena will count as a loss.
Upgrading military buildings will shorten production time and unlock new units.
Upgrading gold and crystal mines can increase production efficiency.
If you are running out of resources, MOJO can be spent as an alternative.
The amount of MOJO required to speed up production depends on the production time.
"If you're invaded, your buildings may catch fire. Burning buildings can't produce resources."
The battle is lost once the castle wall is destroyed.
There are four types of armor: cloth armor, light armor, heavy armor, and hero armor.
There are four types of attacks: normal attack, piercing attack, magic attack, and hero attack.
Normal attack counters light armor. For example, footmen cause more damage to ninjas.
Piercing attack counters cloth armor. For example, archers cause more damage to trolls.
Magic attack counters heavy armor. For example, mages cause more damage to knights.
Cloth armor counters magic attacks. For example, trolls suffer less damage from mages.
Light armor counters piercing attacks. For example, footmen suffer less damage from archers.
Heavy armor counters normal attacks. For example, knights suffer less damage from footmen.
Hero armor counters all non-hero attacks.
Items and spells have durations; they need to be repaired once they are worn out.
The durability of items and spells decreases over time instead of over number of battles fought.
You can spend gold/crystals or MOJOs to repair your items and spells.
The more MOJOs you buy, the bigger the discount.
The Behemoth has the highest health points and defense spells. He hits two rows of enemies at the same time.
"The Berserker has the highest attack points and a range of two blocks. It's recommended to place him on the battlefield."
The Succubus has the longest attack range, enabling her to attack enemies from afar.
Strategic placement of your hero will prevent enemy invasions.
To review battle wins and master battle tactics, select the attack/defense report from the mail icon to check out your combat videos.
Shattering strike is best utilized against melee units.
There are only three slots for spells, so use them wisely.
Unneeded equipment can broken down in the Alchemy Lab or sold at the shop or Altar of Heroes.
There are chances to win MOJOs in the lottery.
Not-for-sale equipment is available through the lottery and Adventure.
Summoning spells can reinforce your units and block enemy invasion in a critical moment.
Scourge of Doom can cause surprising damage.
Build a Portal to access the Fort City.
Players that have established a Fort City can control two heroes.
Besides MOJO, Magic Spar and Tools, Castle City and Fort City resources are controlled independently.
"Castle City and Fort City armies can assist each other's defense."
"When you're attacking other players, you can send in your Fort troops to back you up!"
You can ask your friends to assist your attacks against other players.
You can invite your friends to help defend your castle.
Upgrade your troops and your technology to boost the strength of your army.
"Upgrade your military technology to raise your soldiers' stats."
Upgrade your production technology to raise your gold and crystal production capacity.
Spar can be used to upgrade your technology, strengthen your soldiers, or upgrade your hero medal.
Magic Spar can be won in the Arena, Adventure mode, and promotional events.
Adventure mode levels may drop gems as loot.
Low level gems can be fused into higher level gems in the Alchemy Lab.
"Gems are used to raise the battle stats of your hero's equipment."
Inlaid gems can be dismounted and replaced.
Your gems and fragments are all stored in your Altar of Hero.
"Once you've reached the required amount, your fragments will automatically fuse into the relevant piece of equipment."
You can cut off communications from particularly annoying players by adding them to your Blocked List.
"You can temporarily hold buildings in the box while you're rearranging your city layout."
"Long-range units don't use Heavy Hits as effectively."
Heroes have the highest resistance to Heavy Hits.

string-array.item: Hope these blue-skinned dudes prove useful on the battlefield……

string-array.name: str_task6
string-array.item: We need more units! Construct a Shooting Range to recruit these long-range elvin archers.

string-array.name: str_task32
string-array.item: The Return of Bad Mouth Carl
"Bad Mouth Carl is as persistent as he is vulgar. He's at our gates again, this time with even more troops."

string-array.name: str_task33
string-array.item: Need a medic? Construct a Magic Library to recruit these priests, masters of healing magic.

string-array.name: str_task36
string-array.item: "Shamans can cast powerful magic to accelerate your units' movement. They are best positioned in the center of your troop formation."

string-array.name: str_task37
string-array.item: Even after suffering so many humiliating defeats, Bad Mouth Carl seems to have a never-ending army. Muster up your courage and become a true conqueror.

string-array.name: str_task39
string-array.item: "Archers are powerful, but we're ready to roll in their worst nightmare."

string-array.name: str_task42
string-array.item: Yes, they are terrifying, but with enough gold, you can be their master. Upgrade the Stable to recruit Wolf Riders.

string-array.name: str_task45
string-array.item: Want to freeze your enemies? Recruit these advanced mages, wielders of frost magic.

string-array.name: str_task48
string-array.item: "Taking advantage of different units' strengths and weaknesses is the key to victory. We recommend arranging a combination of knights and archers."

string-array.name: str_task49
string-array.item: We should seize this opportunity to strike while our enemy is on the retreat! The more units we deploy, the greater our chance of victory.

string-array.name: str_task50
string-array.item: Find the Barracks to start recruiting footmen.

string-array.name: str_task51
string-array.item: Beginner units are still very useful. Even great magic spells can be interrupted by a swift arrow. We recommend using archers against mages.

string-array.name: str_task52
string-array.item: Unit combination is very important. We recommend arranging trolls behind footmen to fully utilize the range of their spears.

string-array.name: str_task53
string-array.item: Archers are very powerful long-range units, but they can only weep when faced with knights. We recommend using knights against archers.

string-array.name: str_task54
string-array.item: With Mages on the field, knights find their shining armor about as useful as scrap metal. We recommend using mages against knights.

string-array.name: str_task55
string-array.item: "You say archangels are unstoppable? You've never heard the howls of wolf riders. We recommend using wolf riders against archangels."

string-array.name: str_task56
string-array.item: Need more gold to recruit units? Construct a gold mine and harvest 300 gold. Remember to use your MOJOs to speed things up!

string-array.name: str_task57
string-array.item: "Bad Mouth Carl has chosen a well-defended place to build his fortress, but we can't turn back now. Let's fight!"

string-array.name: str_task58
string-array.item: The Savage Army is coming to raid us again! Remember to select your hero at the bottom left. He or she will prove to be a great help on the battlefield.

string-array.name: str_task59
string-array.item: "Use your hero's special ability wisely and victory will be a breeze. Your ability is ready to use once the icon lights up."

string-array.name: str_task60
string-array.item: "A group of trolls has appeared! Don't worry, we'll beat them as blue as the day they were born, as usual."

string-array.name: str_task61
string-array.item: "You thought you beat the minions of Bad Mouth Carl into submission, but get ready for bad news. They're back with a full army of swords and spears- and even archers!"

string-array.name: str_task62
string-array.item: Watch out! The head of the Savage Army, Bad Mouth Carl, was spotted nearby. He is a well-known outlaw, not to mention the scourge of dentists worldwide. This should be exciting.

string-array.name: str_task63
string-array.item: Help! Enemy soldiers have breached the castle. Hurry, send troops to rescue us!

string-array.name: str_task64
string-array.item: "Various remnants of Bad Mouth Carl's Army are floating around outside the castle like the wisps of his putrid breath. Let's blow them away."

string-array.name: str_task65
string-array.item: We must really be a pain in the gums to Bad Mouth Carl. His troops have snuck up on us again!

string-array.name: str_task66
string-array.item: Bad Mouth Carl arranged a sneak attack and injured many of our villagers. Deploy troops to drive him back.

string-array.name: str_task67
string-array.item: This time they have also deployed a team of healing priests. Hang in there.

string-array.name: str_task68
string-array.item: "After only a few days rest, Bad Mouth Carl is back again. Word is he's after our crystals this time."

string-array.name: str_task70
string-array.item: Carl has swashbuckled his pirate friend, Captain Jack, onto the battlefield to help. Jack is not easy to handle. Be careful this time, my master.

string-array.name: str_task71
string-array.item: With the support of our priests, our army has become unstoppable!

string-array.name: str_task72
string-array.item: A large army of elves are closing in, on the march for vengeance.

string-array.name: str_task73
string-array.item: A horde of Savage Tribe riders are outside the castle! The fog of war hangs heavy over the battlefield.

string-array.name: str_task74
string-array.item: "Who would have thought that Bad Mouth Carl and Captain Jack are brothers? They've ambushed us!"

string-array.name: str_task75
string-array.item: "Even after defeating Carl's outpost units, his army doesn't seem diminished."

string-array.name: str_task76
string-array.item: Long-time no see, Bad Mouth Carl! I can still smell you through that new armor.

string-array.name: str_task77
string-array.item: "Carl is fleeing again! We won't let him get away this time. We'll take down everyone who stands in our way!"

string-array.name: str_task78
string-array.item: "Huh? Even the wicked witch Pandora has come to their aid? Well, hope she doesn't scuff her slippers. Soldiers, charge!"

string-array.name: str_task80
string-array.item: "We've reached a place surrounded by mountains, perfect for Carl’s hideout."

string-array.name: str_task81
string-array.item: "After years of ruthless battle, we're finally ready to look for Bad Mouth Carl's hideout."

string-array.name: str_task82
string-array.item: Pandora is proving more troublesome than expected. Where does she keep all these soldiers!?

string-array.name: str_task83
string-array.item: "The army ahead seems willing to sacrifice their lives for Carl's cause. Fortunately, they are all close-range units, so we should be able to gain an advantage."

string-array.name: str_task84
string-array.item: "They're trying long-ranged units this time. The key is to get close-range troops in quickly and use each unit's weakness to our advantage."

string-array.name: str_task85
string-array.item: "What? An army of Pandoras!? Let's hope this is some sort of magical illusion."

string-array.name: str_task86
string-array.item: They seem unbeatable! Time to appeal to luck.

string-array.name: str_task87
string-array.item: "We're ready to crush this wicked witch! There's no time for hesitation."

string-array.name: str_task88
string-array.item: "This is Jack's fortress. Bad Mouth Carl won't be far after we win this battle."

string-array.name: str_task89
string-array.item: "By getting rid of Carl's wingman, we will take one step closer to victory!"

string-array.name: str_task90
string-array.item: "A pirate's outfit... Captain Jack, we meet again old friend."

string-array.name: str_task91
string-array.item: "A horde of archangels! Bad Mouth Carl's strongest teams are beginning to advance on us."

string-array.name: str_task92
string-array.item: Oh no, a squad of steel giants! Hang in there!

string-array.name: str_task93
string-array.item: "All of Carl's mages are on the move. Where my archers at?"

string-array.name: str_task95
string-array.item: Where are our mages? Prepare your staffs!

string-array.name: str_task96
string-array.item: "Carl is getting irritated. He's sending these troops on a suicide mission."

string-array.name: str_task97
string-array.item: I can already imagine what a chaotic battle this will be!

string-array.name: str_task98
string-array.item: "True heroes always finishes what they start. This time, the only four-letter word we'll hear from Carl is \"Ciao!\""

string-array.name: str_task101
string-array.item: "Captain Jack has come to raid the castle. Careful: more than the scourge of the sea, he's also a master of guerrilla warfare."

string-array.name: str_task102
string-array.item: Clear away the surrounding mercenaries to ensure the safe development of our country.

string-array.name: str_task103
string-array.item: "There's a long and bumpy road ahead, but we're more confident than ever."

string-array.name: str_task104
string-array.item: Arrange close-range units at the front and long-range units at the back for the most basic formation strategy.

string-array.name: str_task105
string-array.item: More experience is gained in more engaging battles.

string-array.name: str_task106
string-array.item: Use shamans to speed up our troops so that they can penetrate all enemy defenses.

string-array.name: str_task107
string-array.item: With these lightning-fast units, our raids against other countries will only get easier.

string-array.name: str_task108
string-array.item: Sound the horn of conquest! The battlefield is merely our playground.

string-array.name: str_task112
string-array.item: "We need a stronger army to break through Bad Mouth Carl's fortress. Time to summon the archangels. Upgrade your Magic Temple to level 4."

string-array.name: str_task113
string-array.item: These steel giants will help clear away any obstacles blocking our road to victory.

string-array.name: str_task116
string-array.item: A horde of trolls has appeared! Shatter their formation with magical spells.

string-array.name: str_task117
string-array.item: The Savage Tribe minions that you just defeated have brought new units to seek revenge!

string-array.name: str_task118
string-array.item: Even though we are outnumbered, we can destroy their fortress if we concentrate on clearing a path to the castle wall.

string-array.name: str_task119
string-array.item: Looks like Bad Mouth Carl is testing us by sending out a scouting team.

string-array.name: str_task121
string-array.item: "Time to put these elves to the test! With their help, we'll crush our enemies."

string-array.name: str_task122
string-array.item: Keep in mind that close-range units are stronger and should be arranged at the front of the formation.

string-array.name: str_task123
string-array.item: "It is vital to stay calm during a battle and cast spells at the right time. Don't waste your hero's mana."

string-array.name: str_task125
string-array.item: "Priests are very weak units. They don't have helmets or armor and must be stationed behind other soldiers for protection."

string-array.name: str_task126
string-array.item: Who are these jumpy green-skinned fellows? Could they be the legendary shaman priests?

string-array.name: str_task127
string-array.item: "Why has our enemies' attack speed increased? It must be the weird spells that the shamans are casting."

string-array.name: str_task128
string-array.item: "That's odd- I was just eating an ice cream. Why is it suddenly snowing outside?"

string-array.name: str_task129
string-array.item: Archers have an advantage in suppressing these Mages. Give them a try.

string-array.name: str_task130
string-array.item: You, hero, have defended your kingdom. Would you tell me your name? It shall be remembered in the annals of history.

string-array.name: str_task131
string-array.item: Tap on your castle and select the formation icon. Arrange your troops in front of the castle to protect it from enemies.

string-array.name: str_task132
string-array.item: A group of mysterious units from the east who cover their faces and wield strange weapons. Upgrade the Shooting Range to level 3 to recruit them.

string-array.name: str_task133
string-array.item: Ow! Those darts are nothing if not annoying. Please - yikes! - dispose of these ninjas quickly!

string-array.name: str_task134
string-array.item: The fallen units will turn into zombies. Fortunately, we have plenty of archers.

string-array.name: str_task135
string-array.item: Defend the fortress and smite the army of zombies.

string-array.name: str_task136
string-array.item: Flowing blonde hair, piercing green eyes, and a heavy bow? Who are these agile new foes?

string-array.name: str_task137
string-array.item: "Pew! Pew! That was close! I'd have lost my ears if I hadn't dodged in time."

string-array.name: str_task139
string-array.item: Open the construction panel, build a Prison Cell, then raid and capture another player to do your labor!

string-array.name: str_task141
string-array.item: Construct a Shooting Range to recruit these elf archers.

string-array.name: str_task142
string-array.item: Want to become a priest? Start by hitting the books- or rather, grimoires.

string-array.name: str_task144
string-array.item: Riders are worth the pain it is to feed these four-legged beasts.

string-array.name: str_task145
string-array.item: "I feel dizzy just looking at all these bookshelves. Don't be surprised if you enter clean-shaven and come out with a long white beard."

string-array.name: str_task146
string-array.item: Ding, Ding, Ding. What time is it? Do these mechanical freaks ever take a break?

string-array.name: str_task147
string-array.item: You need more land to establish a grand empire. Select the windmill to expand your empire.

string-array.name: str_task148
string-array.item: Select the build icon and construct a Gold Mine to start harvesting gold.

string-array.name: str_task149
string-array.item: Select the build icon and construct a Crystal Mine to start harvesting crystal.

string-array.name: str_task150
string-array.item: These blue crystals contain magical powers, so handle with care.

string-array.name: str_task152
string-array.item: Feeling generous? You can help rescue your friend when you see his or her SOS sign is on.

string-array.name: str_task153
string-array.item: Select the shield icon and choose an opponent to fight. You will gain points and advance your rankings.

string-array.name: str_task154
string-array.item: "Don't your friend's resources look tempting? Go ahead, no one is watching."

string-array.name: str_task155
string-array.item: "Everyone who sees it makes the same remark: it's the perfect long-range weapon for killing and destruction."

string-array.name: str_task157
string-array.item: The reappearance of ancient troll machinery has been a nightmare on the battlefield. These machines are merciless and unstoppable.

string-array.name: str_task158
string-array.item: A rain of sharp arrows and steel bullets reaps the lives of countless soldiers.

string-array.name: str_task159
string-array.item: Iron knights charge as steel bullets fly, both whistling like anguished cries on the wind.

string-array.name: str_task160
string-array.item: This iron formation looms like a cloud in the sky, promising another blood rain.

string-array.name: str_task161
string-array.item: "You should make a wish. Huh? Your wish is to survive? Well, that's sort of like wishing for more wishes, isn't it..."

string-array.name: str_task162
string-array.item: A team of giant armored machines combined with powerful magic casters, both ready to strike.

string-array.name: str_task163
string-array.item: Jack has recruited new units armed with advanced weapons onto the battlefield.

string-array.name: str_task165
string-array.item: Bad Mouth Carl has brought his foulness to the front line and rallied his troops to prepare against the intruders.

string-array.name: str_task166
string-array.item: The once unstoppable Jack has never before tasted defeat, a bitter flavor he can quench only with more blood.

string-array.name: str_task167
string-array.item: There is always a strange shadow lurking amongst our enemy. Who is she?

string-array.name: str_task168
string-array.item: A battle-scarred hero is claiming he can teach everyone the true wisdom of war.

string-array.name: str_task169
string-array.item: "Click on the top left player avatar to open the player information page. Click on the signature box to enter your personal greeting, for example, DON'T STEAL MY GOODIES! You can also change your password/avatar or reset your game here."

string-array.name: str_task170
string-array.item: "Click on the shiny statue on the map and select check to open the hero panel. You can drag the items you just won/bought onto the item slots to equip your hero. Doesn't your hero look awesome now?"

string-array.name: str_task171
string-array.item: After building a prison cell, you are ready to capture another player. Select the prison cell on the map and choose an unlucky player to raid.

string-array.name: str_task188
string-array.item: This time, we will nail it!

string-array.name: str_task189
string-array.item: Helping others is another way of helping yourself.

string-array.name: str_task190
string-array.item: I take as much as I please. No more worries about gold and crystals!

string-array.name: str_task192
string-array.item: Protection is crucial for healthy growth. To choose your defense formation, click the fort building, then press the army-shift button. You can set up your castle army now.

string-array.name: str_task193
string-array.item: All for one, and one for all!

string-array.name: str_task194
string-array.item: The perfect fusion of magic and technology, time and space.

string-array.name: str_task195
string-array.item: These mysterious troops are the first sign of new power emerging.

string-array.name: str_task196
string-array.item: Here comes Juster, a black-clothed grim reaper smiling through a veil of blood!

string-array.name: str_task197
string-array.item: Is this a gangster movie or something?

string-array.name: str_task198
string-array.item: "Is that really... Jack? Isn't he already…"

string-array.name: str_task199
string-array.item: Alive or dead, Jack and Carl are always the losers!

string-array.name: str_task200
string-array.item: Somehow, the puppet has reached stage two.

string-array.name: str_task201
string-array.item: The evil forces have crushed the last shackles of the War Spirit. The pinnacle of war is coming!

string-array.name: str_task202
string-array.item: Guess who comes after Carl and Jack?

string-array.name: str_task203
string-array.item: The complete Pandora- what a nightmare!

string-array.name: str_task204
string-array.item: "With the new castle, everything will begin anew. Remember, safety always comes first, so let's start our defense now!"

string-array.name: str_task205
string-array.item: The first step to recruiting footmen is to build some barracks.

string-array.name: str_task206
string-array.item: "OK! Let's shows them who the king of fighters is in the arena."

string-array.name: str_task207
string-array.item: This fort will certainly grow on you when you find the gold mine inside!

string-array.name: str_task209
string-array.item: "Hurry up! Attention! Uniform alteration. Click the Blacksmith, select View, then click the Upgrade button. If your have sufficient resources, don't hesitate to outfit your troops in the latest of defensive fashion!"

string-array.name: str_task210
string-array.item: Our slogan is: faster, farther, and flawlessly accurate!

string-array.name: str_task211
string-array.item: Click on the Wind Shrine, then click View, Upgrade, and then Start Upgrade to upgrade your archers to high-level wizard strikers.

string-array.name: str_task212
string-array.item: New equipment for a truly professional look on the battlefield.

string-array.name: str_task213
string-array.item: For better or for worse, their skin will stay blue.

string-array.name: str_task214
string-array.item: Surprise your enemy on the battlefield with advanced infantry!

string-array.name: str_task215
string-array.item: Get the swiftness of the wind behind us.

string-array.name: str_task216
string-array.item: "You can't see it, but they hold the wind in their hands."

string-array.name: str_task217
string-array.item: "Don't worry about a black sky- it's only a storm of arrows."

string-array.name: str_task219
string-array.item: Time heals all wounds. So, we should probably shorten that time.

string-array.name: str_task220
string-array.item: Let steel and iron cut as one!

string-array.name: str_task221
string-array.item: When their iron boots settle again on this land, the very earth will quake!

string-array.name: str_task222
string-array.item: "It's so wonderful to become so powerful…"

string-array.name: str_task223
string-array.item: When the arcane arts are wielded in their full glory, they will dazzle you beyond all description.

string-array.name: str_task224
string-array.item: Long before freezers, mages relished the great sense of accomplishment of manipulating liquid water into solid ice.

string-array.name: str_task225
string-array.item: Enemies will lose their heads before they even see us!

string-array.name: str_task226
string-array.item: Our adrenaline is pumping. It must be the power granted by our ancestors!

string-array.name: str_task227
string-array.item: Luckily, there are shortcuts to becoming a magic master.

string-array.name: str_task228
string-array.item: Wanna be faster? The shaman will show you the way!

string-array.name: str_task229
string-array.item: Confident enough to run through these newly-equipped footmen?

string-array.name: str_task230
string-array.item: Careful, these arrows are imbued with magical forces.

string-array.name: str_task231
string-array.item: You think a shotgun will make a difference now?

string-array.name: str_task232
string-array.item: No one is faster than my swords!

string-array.name: str_task233
string-array.item: Trained cavalry are speeding past, tearing up the earth.

string-array.name: str_task234
string-array.item: "Ice wizards, attention! Don't let the enemy freeze you out!"

string-array.name: str_task235
string-array.item: An uprising of wolves so powerful, the moon is howling back.

string-array.name: str_task236
string-array.item: Wheels on the Sea of Bodies
Iron wheels floating over clusters of bodies on a sea of blood.

string-array.name: str_task237
string-array.item: The angels are spreading their wings. Their attacks thunder down like angry bolts of retribution.

string-array.name: str_task238
string-array.item: A higher level robot requires a better pilot.

string-array.name: str_task239
string-array.item: Nooooo! How did priests get so tough?

string-array.name: str_task240
string-array.item: "They were never soldiers, but that's how they surprise you."

string-array.name: str_task241
string-array.item: The war changes, but power remains!

string-array.name: str_task243
string-array.item: From high to low and the same way back, the grim reaper never rests.

string-array.name: str_task244
string-array.item: Where there is conviction, there is force.

string-array.name: str_task245
string-array.item: Faced with a wall of iron, moving even an inch forward is pure delusion.

string-array.name: str_task246
string-array.item: "Don't underestimate this battle, or you'll earn a lifetime of I-told-you-so's."

string-array.name: str_task247
string-array.item: Just attack and defend. No problem, right?

string-array.name: str_task248
string-array.item: Magic can kill but also heal.

string-array.name: str_task249
string-array.item: Click the hammer and find the red shelter. This is the best way to raise your population limit.

string-array.name: str_task250
string-array.item: Bandits are constantly hanging around the outskirts of Grand Village. The village mayor has requested that we chase the bandits away for good.

string-array.name: str_task251
string-array.item: In the midst of our crusade, we found that many of the robbers are imperial subjects! We must get to the root of the problem.

string-array.name: str_task252
string-array.item: "It seems that under Larry's tyranny, the people grew desperate and had no choice but to turn to a life of crime. We'll defeat their base camp and appeal to their leader to set things right."

string-array.name: str_task253
string-array.item: "Defeating their leader has proven your strength. They're willing to rise against Larry with you!"

string-array.name: str_task254
string-array.item: "We've discovered a band of Larry's troops stationed in the Iron Forest. Let's check it out."

string-array.name: str_task255
string-array.item: "Their forces are rich in resources. Let's help ourselves and see if we can get some valuable fragments!"

string-array.name: str_task256
string-array.item: "They've slaughtered innocent people in this land! We must stop them!"

string-array.name: str_task257
string-array.item: "Whitewater River is overrun with a strange plague, while Larry's troops remain immune. There's something very wrong here."

string-array.name: str_task258
string-array.item: "It really is Larry's forces making mischief. But to what end? Let's see."

string-array.name: str_task259
string-array.item: "They're sacrificing innocent souls to complete an evil ritual! What dark power is Larry mixed up in? We must put an end to this wild scheme!"

string-array.name: str_task260
string-array.item: Whitewater River has been garrisoned by magical monsters! Defeat them before they can escape!

string-array.name: str_task261
string-array.item: "Whitewater River is still polluted by some straggling bands of soldiers; let's clean them out."

string-array.name: str_task262
string-array.item: "Ne'erfrost Harbor is the largest port in the empire. Control the harbor to control the supply of goods across the country. First, let's defeat the surrounding garrisons."

string-array.name: str_task263
string-array.item: "Ne'erfrost Harbor's surrounding guards are excellently equipped and quite strong. Defeating them won't be easy, but it will give us an important foothold."

string-array.name: str_task264
string-array.item: "Take the harbor control room, and maybe we'll draw our enemy out further."

string-array.name: str_task265
string-array.item: "Clear out the leftover troops surrounding Ne'erfrost Harbor to stabilize the port."

string-array.name: str_task266
string-array.item: "The air over Loeffing Boulevard is still and dead. What has Larry done here? Let's investigate."

string-array.name: str_task267
string-array.item: "The guards of every stronghold on Loeffing Boulevard are holding fast, refusing to emerge. This isn't like their previous strategy. Are they protecting something? We have to get to the Loeffing Boulevard interior."

string-array.name: str_task268
string-array.item: "The source of the plague is before us! Disrupt the ceremony and capture the shaman. Then we can finally find out what Larry's up to!"

string-array.name: str_task269
string-array.item: Our enemy has sent out many small waves of enemies, trying to break our hold on Loeffing Avenue. We must stop them!

string-array.name: str_task270
string-array.item: "Some of the shaman's followers are still trying to restore the ceremony. We'll punish them and their evil creed!"

string-array.name: str_task271
string-array.item: "We've finally returned to the familiar city of Evensnow. Let's cut off their outposts quickly; wouldn't want them to spoil our surprise to Larry."

string-array.name: str_task272
string-array.item: Under siege, William saw one of his old soldiers. Since he has already allied himself with Larry, we have no choice but to fight it out on the battlefield.

string-array.name: str_task273
string-array.item: "Larry has set Pandora free! What an idiot. Defeat Pandora's demon army before they can advance beyond Evensnow!"

string-array.name: str_task274
string-array.item: "Pandora has released scores of demonic soldiers! Let's cast them out!"

string-array.name: str_task275
string-array.item: "We've chased Pandora to Leafy Spring，but it looks like she's left some troops at the entrance to prevent us from following her. Eliminate them!"

string-array.name: str_task276
string-array.item: "Pandora's enchanted armies keep getting stronger and stronger. We better defeat her soon!"

string-array.name: str_task277
string-array.item: "Pandora left two Demon Fangs behind to attack us. We'll have to defeat them before we can continue our pursuit."

string-array.name: str_task278
string-array.item: "Defeat Pandora's reinforcements and we'll cripple her power base."

string-array.name: str_task279
string-array.item: "Pandora has unexpectedly set up an aide-de-camp on guard here, probably to prevent us from entering the valley. She's definitely up to something evil. We can't let her win!"

string-array.name: str_task280
string-array.item: "We're hot on Pandora's trail again. We have to beat the intervening soldiers as quickly as possible and continue the chase!"

string-array.name: str_task281
string-array.item: "Pandora used her magic to summon even more demon soldiers. She's obviously stalling for time. Whatever she's up to, we'll have to beat these demonic units before we can find out."

string-array.name: str_task282
string-array.item: Pandora is opening a portal to the demon realm! Quickly, beat her soldiers and lock that portal down!

string-array.name: str_task283
string-array.item: "The portal's been closed, but some demons still slipped through the cracks into our world. We'll melt them down in Fire Valley!"

string-array.name: str_task284
string-array.item: "Luckily we got the portal closed quickly, but it seems like something unusual is going on at the top of Black Snow Mountain. Let's go check it out."

string-array.name: str_task285
string-array.item: "Even though we cut off the Devil's arrival, the fearsome Magic Dragon made it through instead. Defeat the nearby troops so we can continue onwards."

string-array.name: str_task286
string-array.item: "Magic fire threatens to consume the world! The longer we put it off, the larger the disaster will grow. Don't savor the battle; quickly terminate the demon soldiers on the mountain and rush to face the Magic Dragon!"

string-array.name: str_task287
string-array.item: The Eve of the Last Battle

"We're close to Snowcloak Cliff now, and we can see the Magic Dragon's gigantic outline on the horizon! We can't let the Magic Dragon open the portal again. Let's hurry to him, and to our final battle."

string-array.name: str_task288
string-array.item: "Even though we're exhausted, we don't have much time left. Break through the surrounding soldiers and continue into the wilderness, towards the dragon's lair."

string-array.name: str_task289
string-array.item: The Magic Dragon is still weak from his descent to the mortal plane; we have to act quickly, before he recovers his strength, or no one will be able to stop his great awakening.

string-array.name: str_task290
string-array.item: "This is the Battle that Doesn't End..."
"The Magic Dragon is summoning magical soldiers nonstop. It's an obvious stall tactic, but we can't let these demons get past Snowcloak Cliff!"

string-array.name: str_task291
string-array.item: And It Goes On and On...
"The sheer magnitude of these demonic soldiers is terrifying. They'll keep appearing if we don't defeat the Magic Dragon soon-- we'll have to go directly to his castle!"

string-array.name: str_task292
string-array.item: Before the dragon recovers his full strength, stab him in the heart and end his evil rampage!

string-array.name: str_task293
string-array.item: The people who work here are such weirdos, going on and on about production speed, capacity, and all that other nerd stuff…

string-array.name: str_task294
string-array.item: To prevent enemies from coming and looting our resources, we need to build a Warehouse! The Warehouse can be used to set aside some resources and protect them from raiders.

string-array.name: str_task295
string-array.item: After upgrading the Warehouse, it will have an increased capacity for protecting a greater amount of resources. Please upgrade your Warehouse to level 2.

string-array.name: str_task296
string-array.item: "Give your weapons and armor that elusive element of, 'Ooh, shiny!'"

string-array.name: str_task298
string-array.item: Our fusion gems are getting enormous!

string-array.name: str_task299
string-array.item: If we succeed, this gem will be unrecognizable from its previous form.

string-array.name: str_task300
string-array.item: If one hour can produce this much gold, then one hundred hours…

string-array.name: str_task302
string-array.item: We need a strong castle to put our minds at ease.

string-array.name: str_task303
string-array.item: Mount gems on your weapons and watch them shine with a powerful light.

string-array.name: str_task304
string-array.item: Add a friend, visit each other... And a networking mogul is born!

string-array.name: str_task305
string-array.item: Train with Old Camel, and practice will make perfect through his combat exercises!

string-array.name: str_task306
string-array.item: Establish the bond between your empire and your allies, and never fight alone again!

string-array.name: str_task307
string-array.item: What luck to win so much your first time on the betting floor!

string-array.name: str_task308
string-array.item: Select the Barracks, tap on the upgrade icon and you will recruit your new unit soon!

string-array.name: str_task309
string-array.item: The mission of the alliance is simple: all for one, and one for all!

string-array.name: str_task310
string-array.item: Besides mojo, magician-made hourglasses can be used to make time fly!

string-array.item: Train with Old Camel, and practice will make perfect through his combat exercises!

string-array.name: str_task324
string-array.item: Train with Old Camel, and practice will make perfect through his combat exercises!

string-array.name: str_task325
string-array.item: "Don't your friend's soldiers look tempting? Go ahead, no one is watching."

string-array.name: str_task326
string-array.item: "Don't want to waste time waiting? Select the building under construction and click 'Speedup'!"

string-array.name: str_task327
string-array.item: "Subjects are flocking here after hearing tell of your great kingdom. You'll need more Red-shingled Houses to keep them all!"

string-array.name: str_task328
string-array.item: We need more soldiers, STAT! Maybe building more Barracks would attract more recruits.

string-array.name: str_task329
string-array.item: Yet another gold mine has been discovered. Full coffers are around the corner!

string-array.name: str_task331
string-array.item: Upgrade your Shooting Range to attract mysterious soldiers from the East.

string-array.name: str_task332
string-array.item: Upgrade your mining facilities to get more gold each day!

string-array.name: str_task333
string-array.item: Your subjects demand tomes! MORE TOMES!

string-array.name: str_task334
string-array.item: The mystical secrets housed in the new library are certain to attract an ice-cold mage or two…

string-array.name: str_task335
string-array.item: Better feeding facilities help foals grow up faster.

string-array.name: str_task336
string-array.item: "Direwolf pups need space to roam. Our old barns just won't do!"

string-array.name: str_task345
string-array.item: A true hero can turn the battle around at even the most critical juncture, holding the key to victory in his or her hands.

"Heroes are the core of your power. Placed strategically, they can decide your victory or defeat. The Behemoth is massive wall of muscle and can shield the frontlines; the Berserker also prefers the front, in order to quickly break your enemies' frontline; while the Succubus, with her ranged attacks, is best kept a deadly secret tucked away in the back."

string-array.name: str_task346
string-array.item: One in front, one in back: maintain order in your attack.

"Footmen have an attack range of 1, Trolls of 2, so Trolls should be placed behind Footmen! With a row of Footmen in the front, Trolls in the back, you'll win easily. Reminder: Drag units to the topmost grid to drop a whole row with one move."

string-array.name: str_task347
string-array.item: Arrows swiftly pierce the sky, and still more swiftly, hit bullseye.

"Meet the Archers! They have an attack range of 5, so they're a good choice for your rear flanks. Place your Footmen and Trolls, then try a row of Archers in the back. Your enemy will be pinned in no time!"

string-array.name: str_task348
string-array.item: Our motto: Only the efficient will be sufficient!
"Ninjas can hurl their shurikens at up to 3 targets at once and perform well against Footmen. A first row of Footmen, plus a second row of Trolls, and a third row of Ninjas adds up to one easy win!"

string-array.name: str_task349
string-array.item: "Staffs held high, chanting low, they'll heal your wounds and ease your woe."

"With your Priests' help, you can multiply your units' strength manyfold. If your opponent has 42 Footmen, you only need one row of Footmen, backed by a row of healing Priests, to turn that 42 into nil."

string-array.name: str_task350
string-array.item: Riding high on horseback, stepping over corpse-back, Knights are on the right track!
"Knights are natural masters over Footmen. With a row of Priests behind them, your Knights are even stronger!"

string-array.name: str_task351
string-array.item: Against an enemy so dire, use formations to aim higher.
"Facing an army of valiant Knights, it's easy to feel beat. Try Knights + Priests + Archers for a combined advantage."

string-array.name: str_task352
string-array.item: "Free from heavy armor's vice, we've naught to fear from cubes of ice!"

"Mages' magic attacks are strong against Knights' heavy armor. Trolls and Archers have piercing attack, which tears through the Mages' cloth armor. Pair a frontline of Trolls with a few rows of Archers, and Mages will be a cinch."

string-array.name: str_task353
string-array.item: Be they few or be they many, our skill can best anybody!
"Looking familiar? Don't worry, Old Camel's still got a trick to show you. Put some Archers in the 4th row, followed by a row of Priests, and get ready to see a miracle!"

string-array.name: str_task354
string-array.item: The Savage Army is coming to raid us again! Remember to select your hero at the bottom left. He or she will prove to be a great help on the battlefield.
"Your highness, you have become quite the maestro of the battlefield! You're ready to go on alone. Old Camel will return when you need him."

string-array.name: str_task356
string-array.item: Use mojo or magic hourglasses to speedup your recruitment and call up Footmen faster! Click on your Barracks and select \"Speedup\" to get started.

string-array.name: str_task357
string-array.item: "The evil dragon's been defeated, but peace is only temporary: while the demonic portal is still open, evil can still enter the human world. Our heroes set out to find the only mystical material than can form the seal-- Star Silver.(The Rune frags may drop in each level of the seal adventure)"

string-array.name: str_task358
string-array.item: "En route to Pebblestone Camp, you heard someone calling for help. You can't just sit idly by without lending a hand!(The Rune frags may drop in each level of the seal adventure)"

string-array.name: str_task359
string-array.item: "The gang's agreed to help Brock save the village of Borderton, but first we have to defeat the giant stone men blocking the road!(The Rune frags may drop in each level of the seal adventure)"

string-array.name: str_task360
string-array.item: The Borderton villagers have already been spirited away by the monsters. Time is tight, so we must find their leader! Cut off the head, and the body will die.(The Rune frags may drop in each level of the seal adventure)

string-array.name: str_task361
string-array.item: "We've finally found the monster's leader holed up in Town Hall, but his true face is still a mystery. There's a bad air about this place, and it seems we'll have to fight our way out."

string-array.name: str_task362
string-array.item: Brock offered his guide services to thank us for saving his village. Deadwater Swamp is covered with traps, so stay guarded and keep fighting!

string-array.name: str_task363
string-array.item: Passing through Deadwater Swamp to hunt for Star Silver in Amethyst Mine, we found a dragon blocking the only exit! Slay the poisonous beast!

string-array.name: str_task364
string-array.item: "With Brock's guidance, we reached the depths of Amethyst Mine safely. But while arguing how to forge a seal from Star Silver, Brock blurted out the secret to smelting the strange material……"

string-array.name: str_task365
string-array.item: "Star Silver is the treasure of Amethyst Mine, and it looks like Medusa never learned to share. We'll have to beat her to collect ore for the seal!"

string-array.name: str_task366
string-array.item: Brock set the whole thing up! That was stupid of us, but thank goodness Mona held on to some Star Silver. Now we just need to find where those True Flames are.

string-array.name: str_task367
string-array.item: "We've finally discovered some True Flames, but it looks like the demons don't want us to reach them. Seems like Brock might be around……"

string-array.name: str_task368
string-array.item: Bigger houses means a bigger populace!

string-array.name: str_task369
string-array.item: A strong empire starts with a strong foundation!

string-array.name: str_task370
string-array.item: "It's easy to lose a lot of troops in battle, so keep the recruits coming!"

string-array.name: str_task371
string-array.item: "Trolls are units with a 2-square range. Let's look at how to use them."
"Trolls have an attack range of two and deal moderate piercing damage, but they're not the toughest units. Look how our enemy puts his trolls in the front-- let's take 'em out!"

string-array.name: str_task372
string-array.item: Elven Archers are elegant, yet deadly, able to take down cloth-armored foes from far away.
"Archers have an attack range of 5 and deal piercing damage. Put them in the rear ranks and let them back up their comrades."

string-array.name: str_task373
string-array.item: Ninjas strike fast, launching 3 shurikens at once. Their normal attack is powerful against Footmen.

"Ninjas have an attack range of 4 and can attack 3 targets at once. Their normal attack is a Footman's nightmare. Take care of the first row of Footmen, and the Archers behind them are left vulnerable. You know what to do!"

string-array.name: str_task374
string-array.item: Priests are supportive units that can help your hero and soldiers recover HP.
Priests are a supportive unit. They have no attack strength, but they can heal their allies. They are weak and need to be protected.

string-array.name: str_task375
string-array.item: "Come on! Old Camel's comprehensive battle training is ready to begin!"
"Time to show what you've learned and make some sweet formations! Set your ranks according to unit attack type and range, trying your best to use all units."

string-array.name: str_task376
string-array.item: Knights wear heavy armor, which is strong against normal attacks. They can easily rid themselves of Footmen, clearing the way for greater things!
"Hahahaha, congrats! You've gained a new unit type: Knights. They can breeze through a row of Footmen, since normal attack barely grazes their heavy armor."

string-array.name: str_task377
string-array.item: "Mages are a powerful magical unit. They can freeze their targets, and their magic attacks are a Knight's nightmare."
"Mages are great magic users. Their magic attacks can penetrate heavy armor. Their icey attacks also slow their targets down."

string-array.name: str_task378
string-array.item: Mages are tough! But we can deal with them.
Look at those juiced up mages: they may terrify Knights, but we know their weakness-- Archers.

string-array.name: str_task379
string-array.item: For 5-square ranged attack unit, see the Wolf Rider! He can decimate light-armored foes.
Check out our super strong Wolf Riders! They have normal attack, and an attack range of 5. They can decimate light-armored foes.

string-array.name: str_task380
string-array.item: "Shamans are another type of supportive unit. They can speed up the units in front of them. Let's take a look!"
Shamans are supportive units with no attack strength. They can boost the attack speed of other units and heroes.

string-array.name: str_task381
string-array.item: "Iron Wheels shock with their destructive power. They can bomb 3 far-away units with just one attack, meaning they're great for eliminating supportive units stationed behind other foes."

"We've got a heavy unit, the Iron Wheel! Iron wheels can attack the enemies behind their target simultaneously. Their attacks deal piercing damage, so they'll take care of cloth-armored foes quickly."

string-array.name: str_task382
string-array.item: Archangels! Their magic attacks have a scattering effect, allowing them to attack all the units around their target. Their magic is strong against heavy armor.
Archangels can attack all the units around Knights, but can also take care of a back row of supportive units, or really any kind of unit!

string-array.name: str_task383
string-array.item: Time to impress us with your formation skills!
Come on! High-level units are nothing once you know how to play them against each other. Show us!

string-array.name: str_task384
string-array.item: Troll Cyborgs have strong survival skills, evidenced by their high HP and strong armor. They make great living shields.
"Robot roll call: Cyborgs, we're on! Troll Cyborgs wear heavy armor and have high HP, making them a great shield for other units. Try them out!"

string-array.name: str_task385
string-array.item: A real challenge is here, but Old Camel will see you through!
"It's time to show us your real skill. Make a clean sweep of your enemies!"

string-array.name: str_task387
string-array.item: "Old Camel's giving you a graduation exam!"

string-array.name: str_task388
string-array.item: "Your hero's strengths were forged in the fires of battle, but it's up to you to choose the direct they'll develop in."

string-array.name: str_task389
string-array.item: "If you don't have enough units to launch an attack, you can withdraw the troops that are guarding your castle."

string-array.name: str_task390
string-array.item: Spells are a huge boost to your Heros power. Head to the game store if you want to buy “Scourge of Doom”!

string-array.name: str_task391
string-array.item: Want your castle to grow faster? Try a Double XP card on for size!

string-array.name: str_task392
string-array.item: Need more manpower? Try building a White Column. Itll beautify your city, AND raise your population and castle defense!

string-array.name: str_task393
string-array.item: Hero accidentally offed in battle? Try the “Blood Talisman” to make your hero absorb more enemy HP. Itd be hard to die if you wanted to!

string-array.name: str_task394
string-array.item: Magic Spar contains mystical powers necessary for upgrading your troops and technology, making Spar Mines absolutely essential.

string-array.name: str_task395
string-array.item: The dragon is slain, but the demons havent given up their invasion. The Heroes have planned a counter-attack: Charge the Demon Gate, and push them back once and for all!

string-array.name: str_task396
string-array.item: Just as expected, the Demon Gate is guarded by a dedicated defense force. Show them that they cant stop us!

string-array.name: str_task397
string-array.item: After a courageous battle, weve finally captured the Gate, and can establish a camp for our expedition.

string-array.name: str_task398
string-array.item: Dololos magic renders soldiers unable to battle. We need find and destroy the magical ward that supports his magic attacks!

string-array.name: str_task399
string-array.item: His magic is strongest closest to the center of the ward，but if we can destroy the Magic Tower, we can move forward!

string-array.name: str_task400
string-array.item: Dololo set a trap in Phantasm Forest! Thanks to the magic worms, our troops are totally exposed to Dololo!

string-array.name: str_task401
string-array.item: Now that we know the forest just makes magic worms stronger, we need to get out and regroup!

string-array.name: str_task402
string-array.item: Weve left the forest, but not the magic worms influence. We need to find the weak link in the Demon Army!

string-array.name: str_task403
string-array.item: At a critical moment, our knights make an unexpected choice……

string-array.name: str_task404
string-array.item: Beat Blood Mountain, and you can lock the Demon Gate once and for all. For the safety of humankind, for the sake of our fallen friends… We must win!

string-array.name: str_task405
string-array.item: Dololo finally faces us in person. Defeat Dololo, and the battle is won.

string-array.name: task_daily0
string-array.item: A monarch must login to inspect their holdings daily!

string-array.name: task_daily1
string-array.item: An established military is the most basic requirement of any empire.

string-array.name: task_daily2
string-array.item: Meld the essences of many gems to fuse one more brilliant than ever before!

string-array.name: task_daily3
string-array.item: Challenge the ragtag soldiers and magic beasts of the Conquest to win fragments and magic spar!

string-array.name: task_daily4
string-array.item: Send your troops against another player to capture a slave and get phat loot!

string-array.name: task_daily5
string-array.item: "Send soldiers to assist your friend's defense and their walls will be impregnable!"

string-array.name: task_daily6
string-array.item: Be they our rivals or those of our friends, they must pay!

string-array.name: task_daily7
string-array.item: The glory of the Arena is earned only by piling victory upon victory!

string-array.name: task_daily8
string-array.item: Magic can cut through time, fast forwarding to the moment of completion.

string-array.name: task_daily9
string-array.item: Hide the control icons and use the camera in the upper right corner to share your empire with your friends!

string-array.name: task_daily10
string-array.item: Click on your avatar, then click your invitation code to get more friends playing Little Empire!

string-array.name: task_daily11
string-array.item: Help Your Friend Speed Up Production
Your friends need help producing faster and faster!

string-array.name: task_daily12
string-array.item: Your friend has been captured! You must send an army to rescue them!

string-array.name: task_daily13
string-array.item: "It's lonely on the battlefield. Call some friends over to savor victory together!"

string-array.name: task_daily14
string-array.item: "Accept a friend's invitation to assist attack and help them flatten their enemies!"

string-array.name: task_daily15
string-array.item: No empire can operate without good old gold.

string-array.name: task_daily16
string-array.item: "Crystal is not just a luxury good; it's a resource critical to your empire's development."

string-array.name: str_task355
string-array.item: Our iron-helmed knights are geared up and ready to go.

"O wise king, you're ready to lead troops into battle! You've made Old Camel proud. You'll have to face the remaining challenges alone, but even though can't be by your side, Old Camel will still be listening to your legend in the making!"

string-array.name: str_task406
string-array.item: The hero will not feel lonely in the battle and please build a family for the pets.

string-array.name: task_daily17
string-array.item: The Egyptian Set calls you from the path of the Seal!

string-array.name: task_daily18
string-array.item: Strike back against the demons, defend your homeland, and keep your pet well-fed!

string-array.name: task_daily20
string-array.item: Its a clash of commanders in the heat of battle!

string-array.name: str_task407
string-array.item: "The Demon World appears to be a projection of our world! Everything looks so similar, but so different at the same time. This must be the Demon King's camp."

string-array.name: str_task408
string-array.item: "Even the geography and place names are the same as our world! This must show the Demon's hunger for our world. Powerful guards are stationed at every junction."

string-array.name: str_task409
string-array.item: All of the guards are old enemies, but they are just as strong as ever, and seem to have no memory of our history! Looks like we have a long battle ahead.

string-array.name: str_task410
string-array.item: "Just as expected, the path to Ne'erfrost Harbor is just the same. But, the Demons citizens here seem to keep their distance, glaring with open hostility."

string-array.name: str_task411
string-array.item: Our scouts hve come back with alarming news: The City of Evensnow is guarded by Larry！Is this really a different world?

string-array.name: str_task412
string-array.item: "We defeated Larry, just as before. Before he succumbed, he said something shocking: The Demon World is actually the space within the people of our world's hearts. Demons are the manifestations of our darkest desires, and the gods bring those desires to our world. In truth, the hearts of the people long to be ruled."

string-array.name: str_task413
string-array.item: We found an ancient tablet near Leafy Spring which prophecies that when the desires of the Real World overflow, the Demon World will expand, opening a path to the Real World. The evil dragon Dorck can enter through this path! How will we fight on?

string-array.name: str_task414
string-array.item: William stayed calm in the face of despair. Demons thrive on order. They need someone commander to move forward. Finding a new commander will be their first priority.

string-array.name: str_task415
string-array.item: "Monroe's memory awakened Dorck's true form,an ancient black dragon god! He believes the desire overflowing from the Real World is so powerfully repugnant, the Demons have the power to completely reset the world."

string-array.name: str_task416
string-array.item: Even the ancient gods have no right to judge our world or decide its fate. Righteousness cannot be denied. The evil dragon Dorck must be stopped!

string-array.name: runatt
string-array.item: Dash headlong into target. May inflict Dizzy.

string-array.name: crazy
string-array.item: Raises attack strength and attack speed.

string-array.name: explosion
string-array.item: Body explodes upon death, damaging surrounding enemies.

string-array.name: throughAttack
string-array.item: Attacks may damage all enemies directly to the front.

string-array.name: multipleAttack
string-array.item: Attacks may affect up to 6 units at once.

string-array.name: poisonAttack
string-array.item: Attacks may cause enemies to bleed.

string-array.name: doubleAttack
string-array.item: May throw two bombs with one attack.

string-array.name: groupheal
string-array.item: Chance to heal all surrounding allies.

string-array.name: boltArrow
string-array.item: Shoots on Lighting Arrow upon entering the field, then shoots another after a time.

string-array.name: angelShield
string-array.item: Shields frontline allies from being Dizzy, Frozen, Weakened or Poisoned for a time.

string-array.name: firegun
string-array.item: Chance of dealing extra damage against cloth-armored foes.

string-array.name: damageShield
string-array.item: After your HP falls below a certain point, a ratio of all damage you receive will be dealt back to oncoming units.

string-array.name: fever
string-array.item: "Casts periodically, raising surrounding units' Attack (has no effect on Heroes or support units)."

string-array.name: curse
string-array.item: When attacking, has a chance of inflicting a Curse on enemy soldiers, lowering their chance of Counter and Evasion.

string-array.name: str_hero_orc
string-array.item: A legendary orc who battled against the humans and elves, he lost his jaw and replaced it with steel. He specializes in defense and should be stationed at the front line.

string-array.name: str_hero_sparta
string-array.item: The 300-year-old prince of a long-lost human empire, he bears scars as painful reminders of what he has lost. He specializes in combat and should be stationed at the center.

string-array.name: str_hero_witch
string-array.item: A fallen spirit that wanders between the shadow realms. Consuming souls is her only passion. She has long attack range and should be stationed at the rear.

string-array.name: str_ninja
string-array.item: Hits multiple enemies over a long range.

string-array.name: str_civilian
string-array.item: The symbol of your army. If all your army banners are destroyed, you’ll be defeated. Boosts surrounding units HP.

string-array.name: str_civilian2
string-array.item: The symbol of the Commander. If it’s destroyed, you’ll be defeated. Boosts attack speed of surrounding units.

string-array.name: str_frozentrap
string-array.item: Step on this trap, and surrounding soldiers from both sides will be Frozen.

string-array.name: str_poisiontrap
string-array.item: Step on this trap, and surrounding soldiers from both sides will be Poisoned.

string-array.name: str_weaktrap
string-array.item: Step on this trap, and surrounding soldiers from both sides will be Weak.

string-array.name: str_firetrap
string-array.item: Step on this trap, and surrounding soldiers from both sides will take damage and have their attacks interrupted.
